# Explicarea arhitecturii

Fluxul de licitație:

```text
Bidder
   ↓
Auctioneer
   ↓
MessageProcessor
   ↓
BiddingProcessor
   ↓
Auctioneer
   ↓
Bidder
```

Fluxul conversației private:

```text
UserCommunicationMicroservice — Daria
UserCommunicationMicroservice — Mihai
UserCommunicationMicroservice — Ioana
                    ↓
        ChatStreamProcessorMicroservice
                    ↓
           ChatMasterMicroservice
                    ↓
      numai membrii camerei private
```

